Log:
  MFC r232994:
  - Fix an erroneous invocation of the editline.
  - Fix wrong scaling in the bc.library.
  - Let length(0.000) conform to what gnu bc does.

  PR:	bin/159227
  Submitted by:	AIDA Shinra <shinra at j10n dot org>

